---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy | SIR Saathi">
  <main class="shell content-page">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p>SIR Saathi is designed to give voter guidance without collecting more data than needed.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>No user accounts are required for the MVP.</li>
      <li>No document uploads are required.</li>
      <li>Raw electoral roll PDFs and parsed voter exports are not published in this repository.</li>
      <li>Search results must be scoped, redacted, and rate-limited before public launch.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Final submission and status checks always happen through official ECI, CEO, BLO, or ERO channels.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
